{"tid":311923,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Web][202]尼奧寵物Neopets! 尼臭已易手","createTime":"2017-07-07T04:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:04:49.000Z","uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"30043414db483009beb396cde763ded5e76e2c40","tid":311923,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">流行歐美、最風行的虛擬寵物遊戲!除了養寵物，還有許多小遊戲可以玩哦! 現在就加入尼奧世界吧!簡單、快捷，而且完全免費 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://www.neopets.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a8274bf1\" target=\"_blank\">www.neopets.com</a></span> <img src=\"http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc11/bananaaming/haha-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi213.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fcc11%2Fbananaaming%2Fhaha-3.jpg&h=610ea8b9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YlyuibB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYlyuibB.png&h=f1e41990&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">以尼奧寵物為主軸，延伸發展出尼奧世界</span><br />\r<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尼奧寵物五大目標: <span style=\"color: blue;\">賺錢、養靚寵、收藏物品、練寵戰鬥、參與劇情活動</span></span> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&darr;新手必看,老手必讀&darr;</span></span></strong></div><br />\r入左尼奧 養左第一隻寵 大家唔知道可以做咩 ? 等巴打私人教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r講左養寵先<br />\r<a href=\"http://www.neopets.com/calendar.phtml \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neopets.com%2Fcalendar.phtml%20&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=07cb1c4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neopets.com/calendar.phtml </a><br />\r&uarr;呢個係尼奧世界日曆 多數「限量版寵物」可以係佢地既寵物日到養到 「限量版寵物」詳情:<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=specialpets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dspecialpets&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8d01fa9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=specialpets</a> 其他養寵方法有:孤兒院領養或同人交換<br />\r尼奧二大特別寵(不能於寵物日領養): <img src=\"http://pets.neopets.com/cp/bg85wvqh/1/4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpets.neopets.com%2Fcp%2Fbg85wvqh%2F1%2F4.png&h=f39391b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pets.neopets.com/cp/3jbj 64kr/1/4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpets.neopets.com%2Fcp%2F3jbj%2064kr%2F1%2F4.png&h=3d480051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r左)特雷<br />\r由特雷蛋孵出 一粒海盜特雷蛋 約值200k~300k(20萬~30萬) <img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/mfo_draikegg_pirate.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fmfo_draikegg_pirate.gif&h=e0b205c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r右)狂妄龍<br />\r以前主要由狂妄龍寵物玩伴變出<br />\r現在多數人買魔力海盜狂妄龍絨毛玩具 約值200k~300(20萬~30萬) <img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/plu_krawk_magical_pirate.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fplu_krawk_magical_pirate.gif&h=db38da1c&s={SIZE}\" /> 使用蛻變藥水的話價錢相若"},{"pid":"f91a9515c060feb5b628a83e8eba21fc3bdc817b","tid":311923,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/altador/misc/neopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Faltador%2Fmisc%2Fneopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif&h=826116c9&s={SIZE}\" />[si ze=6]<span style=\"color: gold;\">儲錢篇</span>[/size=6]<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/altador/misc/neopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Faltador%2Fmisc%2Fneopoints_bag_07b7353930.gif&h=826116c9&s={SIZE}\" /></div> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>*每日必按*</strong></s