//i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpaintbrush_water.gif&h=75999fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/maractitepaintbrush.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fmaractitepaintbrush.gif&h=bdf69821&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解人地隻寵顏色咁靚,我就得紅黃藍綠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/paintbrush_pastel.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpaintbrush_pastel.gif&h=13632e18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.c om/items/pot_kacheek_baby.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.c%20om%2Fitems%2Fpot_kacheek_baby.gif&h=96359db8&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_kyrii_rg.gif[/i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_kyrii_rg.gif%5B%2Fi&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d52c34bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_kyrii_rg.gif[/i</a> mg]<img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_meerca_halloween.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_meerca_halloween.gif&h=5af686b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images. neopets.com/items/pot_lutari_pirate.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.%20neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_lutari_pirate.gif&h=59b3609e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/pot_draik_faerie.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Fpot_draik_faerie.gif&h=f1d82da7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images.neopets.com/items/transparentpaintbrush.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.neopets.com%2Fitems%2Ftransparentpaintbrush.gif&h=6e00fb1c&s={SIZE}\" /> </div> 改變寵物顏色的方法，有六種:(1)筆刷、(2)蛻變藥水、(3)變形藥水、(4)實驗室、(5)泉水精靈 (6)特別方法<br />\r例子:<br />\r(1)使用筆刷 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色不變族)</span></em>: <span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色</span>特雷+<span style=\"color: brown;\">殭屍</span>筆刷=<span style=\"color: brown;\">殭屍</span>特雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (2)使用蛻變藥水 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色及變族)</span></em>: <span style=\"color: maroon;\">機械</span>狂妄龍+<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span>奇俐蛻變藥水=<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色奇俐</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (3)使用變形藥水 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色及變族)</span></em>: <span style=\"color: brown;\">巧克力</span>舒特+朦朦豬<span style=\"color: teal;\">變形</span>藥水=<span style=\"color: teal;\">變形</span>朦朦豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (4)使用實驗室 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色或變族，有時加能力)</span></em>: <span style=\"color: red;\">集齊9張</span>神秘實驗室地圖先入得 總約值1M&uarr; (100萬以上 目前市價150萬)<br />\r詳情: <a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=labray\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dlabray&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=760ea0d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=labray</a><br />\r(5)泉水精靈 <em><span style=\"color: orange;\">(變色不變族)</span></em>:<br />\r完成泉水精靈索禮後，免費到彩虹池上色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 詳情:<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=fountain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dfountain&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4ea1c862\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=fountain</a><br />\r(6)特別方法:<br />\r還有其他為寵物改色的魔力物品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r詳情:<a href=\"http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=alteringitems\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jellyneo.net%2F%3Fgo%3Dalteringitems&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4c50a9e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jellyneo.net/?go=alteringitems</a> <div style=\"text-align: center;\">*<span style=\"color: red;\">神</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">秘</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">色</span><span style=\"color: green;\">彩</span>*</div>&quot;機械、趣蛙琪、 MSPP、海綿、果凍、奶油凍、鼻涕、巧克力、黏土、大蒜、冰、熔岩&quot; 詳情:請自行探究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbaedb9bfcc2bdcb0bd136fda9499555d5cc0b1","tid":311923,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/wIkyxCM41PoRLU5WWl/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FwIkyxCM41PoRLU5WWl%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a804f730&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}